Wait… It says [PI] in the title yet it has to do with portforwarding? Another thing is that you say you want to release your server? Do you mean host? Because, releasing something just means uploading it and giving people the download link. And with portforwarding, it includes more than just adding a port to your firewall, you must also add that port to your router as well.
